    <h2>Rotation</h2>

    <h3>Single Target Rotation</h3>
    <ol>
        <li>Keep Consecration active at all times. Recast it if you move out of it or it expires.</li>
        <li>Use Shield of the Righteous as much as possible to maintain uptime and boost armor.</li>
        <li>Use Avenger's Shield on cooldown for Holy damage, interrupts, silences, and Holy Power generation.</li>
        <li>Use Judgment on cooldown for Holy Power generation and applying debuffs (Greater Judgment if talented).</li>
        <li>Use Hammer of the Righteous or Blessed Hammer to generate Holy Power when other abilities are on cooldown.</li>
        <li>Use Word of Glory to heal yourself when needed, ideally with Shining Light procs (free cost).</li>
